Two blocks east on Hastings, you'll find the Elephant and Castle pub which shows Setanta Sports (for the European football fans).	There was an air conditioning on the other side of the street that was quite disturbing.	Wish they had a fan in the bathroom.	Because they don't provide breakfast here at weekends, we ate in the restaurant downstairs.	There is construction work going on but this is not disturbing at all.	Sink/facet combo in bathroom is modern, but facilitates splashing.	Found breakfast and lunch at cafe's in Chinatown, downtown and Granville Island.